readability_reflection: I found concatenation more readable because it was easier just putting together the words with the "+" than using the {}.
comprehension_debugging: Interpolation took a little longer than concatenation but it wasn't that hard and didn't take too long.
preference_rationale: I would prefer concatenation because it is easier to put strings together with the + instead of having to figure out what was inserted using the {}.
learning_curve: Prior experiences helped my understanding because I already knew how concatenation worked so that made it easier to put strings together.
suggestions_improvement: I dont really have any suggestions for improvement because these are fairly basic concepts of strings which are easy to use and understand.
